    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>ShadyVale</strong> is steeped in secrets and mysteries known only to those who created them. Whether you're trying to solve the <strong>mysteries</strong> or escape the <strong>horrors</strong>, there will be an ending—for someone, or something.<br><br>Located somewhere deep in the coastal mountains of the Pacific Northwest. Isolated by sprawling terrain and sheer cliffs, this town is unlikely to be found by anyone unless you are intent of finding it. And on one particular day, after the fog rolled in, its uncertain anyone will ever find it again...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Detective</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Play as Mick</strong>—A man  determined to uncover the secrets of ShadyVale in a Fixed camera style. Use anything and everything at your disposal to get to the bottom of this mystery. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223730/extras/2b052518ab33550af05e116182434a44.poster.avif?t=1748126234\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223730/extras/2b052518ab33550af05e116182434a44.webm?t=1748126234\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223730/extras/2b052518ab33550af05e116182434a44.mp4?t=1748126234\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Survivor</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Play as Alex—</strong> Just trying to escape the first person horrors of ShadyVale with his life. Use your lantern and your wits to elude whatever creatures you come across.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223730/extras/dacd8c9e162f60927656f3a2b284238f.poster.avif?t=1748126234\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223730/extras/dacd8c9e162f60927656f3a2b284238f.webm?t=1748126234\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223730/extras/dacd8c9e162f60927656f3a2b284238f.mp4?t=1748126234\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the P.R.I.S.M to see into another plane of reality.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223730/extras/70cf7de15cca5ee67a6b354da6bdc4c7.poster.avif?t=1748126234\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223730/extras/70cf7de15cca5ee67a6b354da6bdc4c7.webm?t=1748126234\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223730/extras/70cf7de15cca5ee67a6b354da6bdc4c7.mp4?t=1748126234\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your light sources to reveal hidden messages.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223730/extras/c927660ff95b862969f116e832b3a12d.poster.avif?t=1748126234\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223730/extras/c927660ff95b862969f116e832b3a12d.webm?t=1748126234\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223730/extras/c927660ff95b862969f116e832b3a12d.mp4?t=1748126234\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Or to stun your pursuers <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223730/extras/ceabf83361eede285ed8e62a481b32bd.poster.avif?t=1748126234\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223730/extras/ceabf83361eede285ed8e62a481b32bd.webm?t=1748126234\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3223730/extras/ceabf83361eede285ed8e62a481b32bd.mp4?t=1748126234\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul>",
